","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a> の <code>select</code> イベントに対応するイベントハンドラです。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">window.onselect = <em>funcRef</em>;\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef</code> : 関数への参照、または関数式</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ja<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>onselect のテスト<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">.text1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onselect <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> selectText<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">selectText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"select イベントが発生しました。\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cols</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>30<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rows</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\nマウスでこのテキストを選択状態にすると\nonselect イベントが発生し、\nアラートを表示する関数が実行されます。\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注記","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>select</code> イベントは、テキストインプット (<code>&lt;input type=\"text\"&gt;</code>) もしくは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a> 要素のテキストが<em>選択された直後に</em> 発生します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onselect\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">onselect の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onselect","dataURL":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"注記","id":"notes"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"window の select イベントに対応するイベントハンドラです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onselect","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/conflicting/web/api/htmlinputelement/select_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/conflicting/web/api/htmlinputelement/select_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/HTMLInputElement","title":"HTMLInputElement.mozGetFileNameArray()"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select_event","title":"window.onselect"}],"pageTitle":"window.onselect | MDN","noIndexing":true}}